{
    "tiddlers": {
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n      <$image alt=\"Cover\" style=\"\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/images/OEBPS/1999683379936508191_43010-cover.png\"></$image>\n      \n    </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>The Project Gutenberg EBook of Miscellaneous Notes from the Bamboo Leaf\nPavilion, by Yuan-zhi Yao</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>This eBook is for the use of anyone anywhere at no cost and with\nalmost no restrictions whatsoever.  You may copy it, give it away or\nre-use it under the terms of the Project Gutenberg License included\nwith this eBook or online at www.gutenberg.org</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Title: Miscellaneous Notes from the Bamboo Leaf Pavilion</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>Author: Yuan-zhi Yao</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>Release Date: June 22, 2013 [EBook #43010]</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>Language: Chinese</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK MISC NOTES FROM BAMBOO LEAF PAVILION ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by tzu-yi Chuang</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Title: 竹葉亭雜記 (Miscellaneous Notes from the Bamboo Leaf Pavilion)</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>Author: 姚元之 (YAO Yuanzhi (Pinyin; YAO Yuan-chih in Wade-Giles).</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">●卷一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　圣祖仁皇帝之登极也，甫八龄。其时大臣鳌拜当国，势焰甚张，且以帝幼，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 肆行无忌。帝在内，日选小内监强有力者，令之习布库以为戏（布库，国语也，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 相斗赌力）。鳌拜或人奏事，不之避也。拜更以帝弱且好弄，心益坦然。一日入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 内，帝令布库擒之，十数小儿立执鳌拜，遂伏诛。以权势薰灼之鳌拜，乃执于十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 数小儿之手，始知帝之用心，特使权奸不觉耳。使当日令外廷拿问，恐不免激生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 事端。如此除之，行所无事。神明天纵，固非凡人所能测也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　高宗朝，满洲、蒙古王大臣有由上命名者。丰绅济伦本名济伦，丰绅二字，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 上所加也。丰绅，清语有福泽之谓也。御前行走科尔沁王鄂勒哲依忒木尔额尔克</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 巴拜亦系上所名。鄂勒哲依，蒙古语有福之谓也。“哲依”二字急读，音近追上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 声。忒木尔，有寿也。额尔克，铁也。巴拜，宝贝也，音读若罢摆。王为大长公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 主长子。上爱之，幼时期其有福有寿，结实如铁，而又珍之若宝贝，故以是名之。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 一名至十二字，向所罕有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　每年坤宁宫祀灶，其正炕上设鼓板。后先至。高庙驾到，坐炕上自击鼓板，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 唱《访贤》一曲。执事官等听唱毕，即焚钱粮，驾还宫。盖圣人偶当游戏，亦寓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 求贤之意。不知何独于祀灶时唱之？此仪睿皇则不唱，鼓板亦不设矣。盖非国初</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 旧仪也。徐君善庆言。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　嘉庆戊寅九月十六日，圣驾自盛京旋跸。侍卫庆善时年二十二，先期启行，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 私至阳驿，向庄头索租。阳驿去盛京四百余里。未行之先商之敏征，敏乃教之捏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 病请假。特旨用内廷发出，板责庆善六十，发往伊犁；责敏征四十，发往吉林。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 仰见家法之严，不以宗室少贷也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　初圣驾再幸盛京，涓吉七月二十四日启銮，九月回跸。以青龙桥为水冲塌，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 直隶方来青制军受畴请展期，改于二十八日启銮，十月初四日回跸。至盛京礼毕，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 诹吉九月初七日旋跸，乃以阴雨改于十一日，又改十六日。是岁万寿庆节驻跸兴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 隆寺，随扈王大臣官员均于行在行礼。其在京王大臣，有旨概不许差人至行在呈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 递如意贡品。其轮赴行在接驾谢恩者，亦不许携带如意呈递。十月六日开乾清门，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 在京王以下五品京堂以上，俱在门外行庆贺礼。万寿圣节例不进本，戊寅圣驾驻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 跸兴隆寺，办事处奉旨传知各衙门：“应行呈奏事件，仍由报呈递，不可因恭遇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 圣节以至耽延。”圣人之勤如此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　今上即位初，御史多有条陈弹奏时事者。下军机大臣及部议时，上多裁去衔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 名及折尾年月，或条陈数事只议一事，则裁去前后之文，不欲令人知之，恐其取</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 怨也。圣主矜恤言官至意如此。湖北袁道长铣陈奏一折，闻有十事。上裁出核赋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 课、平刑法、广教化三条下大臣会议，余俱留中，不知何事也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　上即位，内府循例备御用砚四十方，砚皆镌“道光御用”四字。上以所备过</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 多，闲置足惜，因命分赐诸臣。英协揆师得其三焉。圣人之俭如此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　御用笔，向皆选取紫毫之最硬者方得奏进。笔管皆镌“天章”、“云汉”等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 字。上以其不合用，命英协揆（时为户部尚书。）以外间习用者进试之，取纯羊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 毫、兼毫二种，命仿此制造。复以管上镌字每多虚饰，命以后各视其笔，但镌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>“纯羊毫”、“兼毫”字而已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　内廷召见，年老大臣颇以升阶登降为苦。道光八年，有“嗣后凡文武大臣年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 逾六十五岁者，准由内右门出入”之旨。道光二十四年十一月二十八日，上念前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 旨于带领引见诸老臣未经分晰，因再准文武三品以上年逾六十五者，遇养心殿带</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 领引见，一体由内右门出入。体恤老臣之恩如此。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　圆明园召见，向在勤政殿。三楹桶扇洞开，殿中有横桶分前后焉。殿东有套</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 间曰东书房，无前廊。夏日召见在殿中，春秋则在书房。书房门向东，前加牌杈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 臣工等由东首台阶上进殿，过横桶，转牌杈，向南稍东即南向跪，则面圣矣。此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 地不大，盖截书房北段为小间。北墙有桶扇门，驾由此出入，是以上面北坐也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 丁酉冬，将书房添前廊，南向开门，北安窗，炕倚窗，设御座炕之西头。东南向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 窗间设大玻璃，以防苑外人窃听。圣人防闲之严如此。臣工由殿外南向之门入见，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 自戊戌正月始也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　御门日遇忌辰，刑部不进本，例也。韩桂林司寇封在署时，问同列曰：“是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 日无本，我辈仍照旧随班上殿否？”众皆不记忆。呼本房笔帖式问之，以其专司</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 是事，知之必悉也。笔帖式但对以总理捧本入殿，众堂官俱随上殿。再问，复如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 是对焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　御门吉庆事也，故向无左迁者。每岁入春，初次例不进刑部本，为其非吉事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 耳。丙戌二月十六日御门，同年朱大京兆为弼调补府丞。盖宗人府丞三品，京兆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 亦三品，上以对品故调之。然府丞差二级矣。后有日者张云征至都，朱少君以八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 字属推，张云：“本年官运大不利，不见风波亦当镌两级。”盖其命定如此。然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 御门降官，向所少有也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　贤良门外有河，河有桥，式如弓背。上看箭，鹄设于桥西河边，射者立桥北，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 北向而射。每发矢，上右顾以视其中否。岁己亥将桥拆平，鹄于桥南对上设焉；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 射者立桥北，面向西而射，以免上右顾之烦也。谈风水者谓此桥架河上如弓之有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 靶，今拆平则弓去靶矣，恐武不振。明年有英夷之扰，其果以是欤？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　圆明园福海之东有同乐园，每岁赐诸臣观剧于此。高庙时，每新岁园中设有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 买卖街，凡古玩估衣以及茶馆饭肆，一切动用诸物悉备，外间所有者无不有之，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 虽至携小筐卖瓜子者亦备焉。开店者俱以内监为之。其古玩等器，由崇文门监督</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 先期于外城各肆中采择交入，言明价值，具于册。卖去者给值，存者归物。各大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 臣至园，许竞相购买之。各执事官退出后，日将晡，内宫亦至其肆市物焉。其执</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 事等官，俱得集于酒馆饭肆哺啜，与在外等。馆肆中走堂者，俱挑取外城各肆中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 之声音响亮、口齿伶俐者充之。每俟驾过店门，则走堂者呼茶，店小二报账，掌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 柜者核算，众音杂逻，纷纷并起，以为新年游观之乐。至燕九日始辍。盖以九重</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 欲周知民间风景之意也。造办处笔帖式徐君善庆每岁入直，言之最详。晚间仍备</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 嘎嘎灯焉。嘉庆四年此例停止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　庆隆舞，每岁除夕用之。以竹作马头，马尾彩缯饰之，如戏中假马者。一人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 踊高赶骑假马，一人涂面身著黑皮作野兽状，奋力跳跃，高し者弯弓射。旁有持</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 红油簸箕者一人，箸刮箕而歌。高超者逐此兽而射之，兽应弦毙，人谓之“射妈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 狐子”。此象功之舞也。有谓此即古大傩之意，非也。闻之盛京尹泰云：“达呼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 尔居黑龙江之地，从古未归王化。彼地有一种兽，不知何名，喜啮马腿，达呼尔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 畏之倍于虎，不敢安居。国初时，曾至彼地，因著高赶骑假马，竟射杀此兽。达</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 呼尔以为神也，乃归诚焉。因作是舞。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>　　圆明园宫门内正月十五放和盒，例也。即烟火盒子，大架高悬。一盒三层：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 第一层“天下太平”四大字；二层鸽雀无数群飞，取放生之意；三层小儿四人击</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 秧歌鼓，唱秧歌，唱“太平天子朝元日，五色云中驾六龙”一首。惟其时余观之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 朝阳满地，不见灯光矣。后停止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　王建《宫词》：“每遍舞头分两向，太平万岁字当中。”《居易录》云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p>“今外国犹传其制。”引郑麟趾《高丽史》云“教坊奏王母队歌舞，一队五十五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 人，舞成四字，或‘君王万岁’、或‘天下太平’。此其遗意”云云。今圆明园</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 正月十五日，筵宴外藩，放烟火，转龙灯。其制，人持一竿，竿上横一竿，状如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 丁字，横竿两头系两红灯。按队盘旋，参差高下如龙之宛转。少顷，则中立向上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 排列“天下太平”四字。当亦前人遗意耶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　旧库内陈物堆积，有明代物。年久无用，发崇文门变价。内有朝靴，以彩缯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 锦缎攒集而成，似缂丝。前作虎形，以皮，金作睛。屈曲者为云气，五色迷离，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 如庙中神象所著者。亦有缂丝者，乃明帝之御物也。或朝、或祀、或晏居，正不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 知何时著此耳？岂明制当如此耶？俟再考。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　年节王大臣呈进如意，取兆吉祥之义也，自雍正年间举行。嘉庆元年，贝勒、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 贝子、公等以至部院侍郎、散秩大臣、副都统俱纷纷呈进两分。于是定以限制：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 凡遇元旦、万寿及庆节，唯宗室亲王、郡王、满汉大学土、尚书始准呈进，其余</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 一概不准。外省盐、关、织造，向有年例办进备赏等物，亦止准备进一分。时苏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 司空楞额为两淮盐政，于例进风猪肉一百块、皮糖八匣，加倍进呈，掷还一半，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 仍处分之。而如意之例，后又减去庆节一次。至己未，则并王公大臣督抚等呈进</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 之例，悉行禁止焉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　御用时宪书写本名曰“上书”。首页节气，次页次年神、方位，三页列二十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 花甲子，四页列六合，末二页纪年，与外本同。每日于五行下注明阴阳。于除危</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 后添注“宝”、“义”、“专”、“制”、“伐”五字，五行生克之谓也。上生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 下为宝，如甲午木生火。下生上为义，如辛丑土生金。上下同宫为专，如戊戌同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 属土。上克下为制，如庚寅金克木。下克上为伐，如壬辰土克水之类。其义不过</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 阴阳刚柔之理耳，于用事宜忌无关。又每日但注吉神，不注恶煞。每日宜忌及款</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 识俱与颁行本不同。今列其式于左，亦多识之一端也。某</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　上某</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　弦日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　某某申</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　刻时子水阳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　义</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　开</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　角</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　东阴天五宝相金天玉兵益生月岁吉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　风神后富光日匮巫宇福后气恩德神</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　解司时天临三天福吉要青不四月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　冻命阳喜日合恩德期安龙将相德</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　候福时敬天岁六兵五天绩时母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　生德安医德仪宝合赦世阳仓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　圣ㄞ普天合金守官三明兵天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　心马护马日堂日日日堂吉德</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　德</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　合</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　针病</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　栽纳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-f09fcd twpub-d87247aca05a87fe-6b4cd0\"><p> 　　营结</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/d87247aca05a87fe/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
